@startuml Sequence_Recruiter_Applications
title Nhà Tuyển Dụng - Xử Lý Đơn Ứng Tuyển

actor Recruiter as "👔 Recruiter"
participant FrontEnd as "Frontend\nApp"
participant ApplicationService as "Application\nService"
database Database as "Database"

== Danh Sách Đơn ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click "Đơn ứng tuyển"
FrontEnd -> ApplicationService: GET /api/applications/recruiter?page=0&size=20
ApplicationService -> Database: Query don_ung_tuyen (recruiter's jobs)
Database --> ApplicationService: Return list
ApplicationService --> FrontEnd: Applications list
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: Hiển thị danh sách

== Xem Chi Tiết Đơn ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click vào đơn
FrontEnd -> ApplicationService: GET /api/applications/{applicationId}
ApplicationService -> Database: Get application details
Database --> ApplicationService: Details
ApplicationService --> FrontEnd: Full info
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: Xem chi tiết

== Xem CV ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click "Xem CV"
FrontEnd -> ApplicationService: GET /api/applications/{applicationId}/cv-snapshot
ApplicationService -> Database: Get banSaoCvUrl
Database --> ApplicationService: CV URL
ApplicationService --> FrontEnd: PDF URL
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: Open PDF

== Xem Lịch Sử Trạng Thái ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click "Lịch sử"
FrontEnd -> ApplicationService: GET /api/applications/{applicationId}/history
ApplicationService -> Database: Query lich_su_trang_thai
Database --> ApplicationService: History
ApplicationService --> FrontEnd: Timeline data
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: Hiển thị timeline

== Cập Nhật Trạng Thái ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click "Cập nhật trạng thái"
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Show status dropdown
Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Chọn status mới
FrontEnd -> ApplicationService: PATCH /api/applications/{applicationId}/status\n(trangThaiMoi)
ApplicationService -> Database: Update don_ung_tuyen
Database --> ApplicationService: OK
ApplicationService -> Database: Create lich_su_trang_thai
Database --> ApplicationService: OK
ApplicationService --> FrontEnd: Updated
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: ✅ Cập nhật trạng thái

== Từ Chối Đơn ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click "Từ chối"
Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Gửi thông báo từ chối
FrontEnd -> ApplicationService: PATCH /api/applications/{applicationId}/reject\n(reason)
ApplicationService -> Database: Update status = TU_CHOI
Database --> ApplicationService: OK
ApplicationService --> FrontEnd: Rejected
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: ✅ Từ chối thành công

@enduml
